---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Total Fitness Mérida · Gimnasio con costales de boxeo"
  description="Pesas, cardio y costales de boxeo bajo un mismo techo. Entrena completo con el coach Gabriel. ⭐ 4.4 con 25 reseñas en Google. Escríbenos por WhatsApp."
  slug="total-fitness-merida"
  ogImage="/total-fitness-merida/img/foto_2.jpg"
  fonts="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Khand:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
  favicon="🥊"
  themeColor="#17181a"
  whatsapp={"https://wa.me/529999459125"}
  telefono={"999 945 9125"}
  mapsUrl={"https://maps.google.com/?cid=12429856129316360359&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA"}
>
  <main class="tf">

    <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="hero-bg" style="background-image:url(/total-fitness-merida/img/foto_2.jpg)" role="img" aria-label="Área de pesas y máquinas de Total Fitness Mérida"></div>
      <div class="hero-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="heavybag" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="hb-chain"></div>
        <div class="hb-body">
          <div class="hb-strap"><span>Total Fitness</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrap hero-content">
        <p class="stamp reveal">La casa de los campeones</p>
        <p class="kicker reveal">🥊 Gimnasio en Mérida, Yucatán</p>
        <h1 class="poster reveal">
          <span class="l1">Total</span>
          <span class="l2">Fitness</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="tagline reveal">Pesas, cardio y <strong>costales de boxeo</strong> bajo un mismo techo. Aquí se entrena completo — y se suda de verdad.</p>

        <a class="chip reveal" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=12429856129316360359&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="star" aria-hidden="true">★</span> 4.4 · 25 reseñas en Google
        </a>

        <div class="cta-row reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-solid" href="https://wa.me/529999459125" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-8.6 15.1L2 22l5.1-1.3A10 10 0 1 0 12 2zm0 18.2c-1.5 0-3-.4-4.3-1.2l-.3-.2-3 .8.8-2.9-.2-.3A8.2 8.2 0 1 1 12 20.2zm4.6-6.1c-.3-.1-1.5-.7-1.7-.8-.2-.1-.4-.1-.6.1-.2.3-.6.8-.8 1-.1.2-.3.2-.5.1a6.7 6.7 0 0 1-3.4-3c-.3-.4 0-.5.2-.7l.4-.5c.1-.2.2-.3.3-.5v-.5c0-.1-.5-1.3-.7-1.8-.2-.5-.4-.4-.6-.4h-.5c-.2 0-.5.1-.7.3-.3.3-.9.9-.9 2.2s.9 2.5 1 2.7c.1.2 1.8 2.8 4.4 3.9.6.3 1.1.4 1.5.6.6.2 1.2.2 1.6.1.5-.1 1.5-.6 1.7-1.2.2-.6.2-1.1.2-1.2l-.4-.3z"/></svg>
            Escríbenos por WhatsApp
          </a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=12429856129316360359&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 0-7 7c0 5.2 7 13 7 13s7-7.8 7-13a7 7 0 0 0-7-7zm0 9.5A2.5 2.5 0 1 1 12 6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0 5z"/></svg>
            Cómo llegar
          </a>
        </div>

        <dl class="datos reveal">
          <div><dt>4.4 <span aria-hidden="true">★</span></dt><dd>calificación real en Google</dd></div>
          <div><dt>25</dt><dd>reseñas de clientes</dd></div>
          <div><dt>5–23h</dt><dd>lunes a viernes · sábado 7–14h</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Divisor firma: cuerdas de ring -->
    <div class="ropes" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="ropes-post"></div>
      <div class="ropes-lines"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
      <div class="ropes-post"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ ROUND 01 · QUIÉNES SOMOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="nosotros">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">Round 01 · Quiénes somos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Aquí se entrena, <span class="rojo">se suda</span> y se suelta el golpe</h2>
        <div class="about-grid reveal">
          <div class="about">
            <p>Somos <strong>Total Fitness Mérida</strong>, un gimnasio pensado para que entrenes completo sin andar batallando: área de pesas, cardio y, para quien quiera soltar el golpe, costales de boxeo — algo que no todos los gimnasios de la ciudad tienen.</p>
            <p>Tal vez no somos el gimnasio con más fierros de Mérida, pero sí de los mejor puestos: todo ordenado, con clima y gente que se nota que sabe tratar bien a quien entra. Si quieres entrenamiento guiado, pide una sesión con el <strong>coach Gabriel</strong> — nuestros clientes lo ponen entre los mejores que hay.</p>
            <p>Ven a conocernos. Abrimos temprano, cerramos tarde, y aceptamos tarjeta para que no batalles con efectivo.</p>
          </div>
          <figure class="side-photo">
            <img src="/total-fitness-merida/img/foto_4.jpg" alt="Recepción y área de suplementos de Total Fitness Mérida" loading="lazy" width="835" height="1100" />
            <figcaption>Recepción · área de suplementos</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ ROUND 02 · QUÉ HAY PARA ENTRENAR ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="instalaciones">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">Round 02 · Qué hay para entrenar</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Todo lo que necesita <span class="rojo">tu rutina</span></h2>

        <div class="offer-grid reveal">
          <ol class="offer">
            <li>
              <span class="glove" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
              <div><h3>Área de pesas y máquinas</h3><p>Suficientes para entrenar completo, sin líneas ni esperas.</p></div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="glove" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
              <div><h3>Costales de boxeo</h3><p>Para meterle a la bolsa, sacar estrés y sumar un cardio distinto.</p></div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="glove" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
              <div><h3>Coaching con Gabriel</h3><p>Rutinas guiadas por un coach que sus clientes recomiendan a ojos cerrados.</p></div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="glove" aria-hidden="true">04</span>
              <div><h3>Zona de cardio</h3><p>Caminadoras, bici y remo para calentar o rematar el entrenamiento.</p></div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="glove" aria-hidden="true">05</span>
              <div><h3>Instalaciones con clima</h3><p>Para entrenar cómodo, incluso en pleno calor de Mérida.</p></div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="glove" aria-hidden="true">06</span>
              <div><h3>Pagas como quieras</h3><p>Aceptamos tarjeta, no solo efectivo.</p></div>
            </li>
          </ol>

          <figure class="showcase-photo">
            <img src="/total-fitness-merida/img/foto_5.jpg" alt="Zona de entrenamiento funcional de Total Fitness Mérida" loading="lazy" width="942" height="1100" />
            <figcaption>Zona de entrenamiento funcional</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>

        <div class="corner-quote reveal">
          <p class="corner-tag">🥊 Del rincón del coach</p>
          <blockquote>«Pidan entrenamiento con Gabriel de los mejores coach que hay. El gym tiene costales de boxeo. Buenas instalaciones con clima»</blockquote>
          <p class="corner-autor">— Eric Martínez, reseña en Google</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ ROUND 03 · RESEÑAS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="resenas">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">Round 03 · Lo que dicen</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal"><span class="rojo">4.4 de 5</span> en 25 reseñas</h2>
        <div class="reviews reveal">
          <figure class="rev">
            <div class="rev-stripe" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>«…tienen más que suficientes para entrenar además de que todo esta super ordenado y las personas son muy amables. Recomendadisimo»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Montserrat Casares</strong><span>Hace un año · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rev">
            <div class="rev-stripe" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>«Pidan entrenamiento con Gabriel de los mejores coach que hay. El gym TIENE COSTALES DE BOXEO. Buenas instalaciones con clima»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Eric Martínez</strong><span>Hace 11 meses · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rev">
            <div class="rev-stripe" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="4 estrellas">★★★★☆</p>
            <blockquote>«Excelente opción si estás lejos de Valladolid…»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Manuel Chávez</strong><span>Hace 8 meses · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="center reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=12429856129316360359&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Leer más reseñas en Google</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ ROUND 04 · UBICACIÓN Y HORARIOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="ubicacion">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">Round 04 · Dónde y cuándo</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Te esperamos <span class="rojo">en la 49</span></h2>
        <div class="ubica reveal">
          <div class="ubica-info">
            <p class="dir">Calle 49 #728, con Av. 128<br />97227 Mérida, Yucatán</p>
            <a class="btn btn-solid btn-sm" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=12429856129316360359&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Abrir en Google Maps</a>
            <h3 class="horario-titulo">Horario del gym</h3>
            <table class="horarios">
              <tbody>
                <tr data-dia="1"><th scope="row">Lunes</th><td>5:00–23:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="2"><th scope="row">Martes</th><td>5:00–23:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="3"><th scope="row">Miércoles</th><td>5:00–23:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="4"><th scope="row">Jueves</th><td>5:00–23:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="5"><th scope="row">Viernes</th><td>5:00–23:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="6"><th scope="row">Sábado</th><td>7:00–14:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="0"><th scope="row">Domingo</th><td>Cerrado</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="mapa-col">
            <div class="mapa">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=Total%20Fitness%20M%C3%A9rida%2C%20Calle%2049%20728%2C%20con%20Av%20128%2C%2097227%20M%C3%A9rida%2C%20Yucat%C3%A1n%2C%20M%C3%A9xico&output=embed"
                title="Mapa: Total Fitness Mérida"
                loading="lazy"
                referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
                allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
            <figure class="facade-photo">
              <img src="/total-fitness-merida/img/foto_3.jpg" alt="Fachada del local de Total Fitness Mérida" loading="lazy" width="1100" height="825" />
              <figcaption>Así nos vas a encontrar</figcaption>
            </figure>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ CTA FINAL ============ -->
    <section class="banda">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2 class="banda-title">¿Listo para el primer round?</h2>
        <p class="banda-sub">Pesas, cardio o costales — tú eliges cómo empiezas. Escríbenos y te decimos cómo entrarle.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn btn-dark" href="https://wa.me/529999459125" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp directo</a>
          <a class="btn btn-dark-ghost" href="tel:+529999459125">Llamar · 999 945 9125</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
    <footer class="pie">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="pie-logo">Total Fitness Mérida</p>
        <p class="pie-dato">Gimnasio · Calle 49 #728, con Av. 128, 97227 Mérida, Yucatán</p>
        <p class="pie-dato"><a href="tel:+529999459125">999 945 9125</a> · <a href="https://wa.me/529999459125" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a></p>
        <p class="pie-mini">Lunes a viernes 5:00–23:00 · Sábado 7:00–14:00 · Domingo cerrado</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "HealthClub",
    "name": "Total Fitness Mérida",
    "telephone": "+529999459125",
    "url": "https://demos.ivang.mx/total-fitness-merida",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "Calle 49 728, con Av 128",
      "addressLocality": "Mérida",
      "addressRegion": "Yucatán",
      "postalCode": "97227",
      "addressCountry": "MX"
    },
    "aggregateRating": {
      "@type": "AggregateRating",
      "ratingValue": "4.4",
      "reviewCount": "25"
    },
    "openingHours": ["Mo-Fr 05:00-23:00", "Sa 07:00-14:00"]
  }
  </script>

  <style is:global>
    :root {
      --carbon: #17181a;
      --panel: #1e2023;
      --rojo: #b91c1c;
      --rojo-bright: #d92727;
      --hueso: #e7e2d9;
      --gris: #3a3d42;
      --muted: #9a9790;
      --line: rgba(231, 226, 217, 0.14);
      --display: "Khand", "Arial Narrow", sans-serif;
      --body: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--carbon);
      color: var(--hueso);
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: clip;
    }

    .tf ::selection { background: var(--rojo); color: var(--hueso); }
    .tf a:focus-visible,
    .tf .btn:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid var(--rojo-bright);
      outline-offset: 3px;
    }

    .wrap { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

    /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 38px);
      min-height: calc(100svh - 38px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 56px 0 44px;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center 32%;
      filter: grayscale(0.55) contrast(1.15) brightness(0.55);
    }
    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(120% 90% at 12% 0%, rgba(185, 28, 28, 0.38), transparent 55%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(23, 24, 26, 0.35) 0%, rgba(23, 24, 26, 0.96) 88%);
    }
    .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; }

    .stamp {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      border: 2px solid var(--rojo-bright);
      border-radius: 999px;
      transform: rotate(-3deg);
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--rojo-bright);
    }
    .kicker {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0 0 14px;
    }
    .poster {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--display);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 0.86;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .poster .l1 {
      font-size: clamp(44px, 13vw, 118px);
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--hueso);
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    .poster .l2 {
      font-size: clamp(78px, 21vw, 196px);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--rojo-bright);
      letter-spacing: 0.005em;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .tagline {
      font-size: clamp(18px, 4.4vw, 23px);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--hueso);
      max-width: 36ch;
      margin: 22px 0 18px;
    }
    .tagline strong { color: var(--rojo-bright); font-weight: 600; }

    .chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--hueso);
      text-decoration: none;
      background: rgba(231, 226, 217, 0.05);
    }
    .chip .star { color: var(--rojo-bright); }
    .chip:hover { border-color: var(--rojo-bright); }

    .cta-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; margin: 24px 0 0; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 19px;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
    .btn-solid { background: var(--rojo); color: var(--hueso); }
    .btn-solid:hover { background: var(--rojo-bright); }
    .btn-ghost { border: 2px solid var(--line); color: var(--hueso); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--rojo-bright); color: var(--rojo-bright); }
    .btn-sm { font-size: 16px; padding: 12px 18px; }

    .datos {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 40px 0 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
    .datos dt {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(22px, 5.6vw, 36px);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--hueso);
    }
    .datos dt span { color: var(--rojo-bright); }
    .datos dd { margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.4; }

    /* ---------- BOLSA DE BOXEO (firma, solo desktop) ---------- */
    .heavybag {
      display: none;
      position: absolute;
      right: 6%;
      top: 8%;
      z-index: 1;
      width: 128px;
      transform-origin: top center;
      animation: sway 5.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .hb-chain {
      width: 3px;
      height: 46px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gris) 0 6px, transparent 6px 12px);
    }
    .hb-body {
      position: relative;
      width: 128px;
      height: 280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-radius: 64px / 100px;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #2b2d31 0%, #1c1d20 70%);
      border: 2px dashed rgba(231, 226, 217, 0.18);
      box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }
    .hb-strap {
      position: absolute;
      left: -14px;
      right: -14px;
      top: 44%;
      height: 32px;
      background: var(--rojo);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transform: rotate(-1.5deg);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    }
    .hb-strap span {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--hueso);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    @keyframes sway {
      0%, 100% { transform: rotate(-2.5deg); }
      50% { transform: rotate(2.5deg); }
    }

    /* ---------- CUERDAS DE RING (firma, divisor) ---------- */
    .ropes {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .ropes-post {
      width: 10px;
      height: 34px;
      background: var(--gris);
      border-radius: 2px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .ropes-lines { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 7px; padding: 0 6px; }
    .ropes-lines span {
      display: block;
      height: 3px;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, var(--rojo) 0 22px, var(--hueso) 22px 26px, var(--rojo) 26px 48px);
      opacity: 0.85;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    .ropes-lines span:nth-child(2) { opacity: 0.55; }
    .ropes-lines span:nth-child(3) { opacity: 0.3; }

    /* ---------- SECCIONES ---------- */
    .sec { padding: 72px 0; }
    .sec-panel { background: var(--panel); }
    .sec-kicker {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--rojo-bright);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .sec-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: clamp(34px, 8.5vw, 62px);
      line-height: 0.98;
      margin: 0 0 30px;
      color: var(--hueso);
    }
    .sec-title .rojo { color: var(--rojo-bright); }

    /* ---------- QUIÉNES SOMOS ---------- */
    .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 30px; align-items: start; }
    .about p { max-width: 62ch; margin: 0 0 18px; color: #cfc9bd; }
    .about strong { color: var(--hueso); }
    .side-photo, .showcase-photo, .facade-photo {
      margin: 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 2px dashed rgba(231, 226, 217, 0.18);
    }
    .side-photo img, .showcase-photo img, .facade-photo img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      filter: grayscale(0.35) contrast(1.08) saturate(0.9);
      aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    }
    .facade-photo img { aspect-ratio: 4 / 3; }
    .side-photo figcaption, .showcase-photo figcaption, .facade-photo figcaption {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    }

    /* ---------- INSTALACIONES ---------- */
    .offer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 34px; align-items: start; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .offer { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: grid; gap: 0; }
    .offer li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: baseline;
      padding: 18px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .offer li:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .glove {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--rojo);
      color: var(--hueso);
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .offer h3 {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 21px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
      color: var(--hueso);
    }
    .offer p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 15px; }

    .corner-quote {
      border-left: 4px solid var(--rojo);
      padding: 4px 0 4px 22px;
      max-width: 62ch;
    }
    .corner-tag {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--rojo-bright);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .corner-quote blockquote {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--hueso);
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .corner-autor { margin: 0; font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--muted); }

    /* ---------- RESEÑAS ---------- */
    .reviews { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 18px; margin: 0 0 30px; }
    .rev {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--hueso);
      color: #1c1a16;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }
    .rev:nth-child(odd) { transform: rotate(-0.4deg); }
    .rev:nth-child(even) { transform: rotate(0.4deg); }
    .rev-stripe {
      height: 7px;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, var(--rojo) 0 10px, #1c1a16 10px 20px);
    }
    .rev-stars { color: var(--rojo); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; margin: 16px 20px 0; }
    .rev blockquote { margin: 8px 20px 14px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.55; font-weight: 500; }
    .rev figcaption { margin: 0 20px 18px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
    .rev figcaption strong { font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
    .rev figcaption span { font-size: 13px; color: #6f6a5e; }
    .center { text-align: center; }

    /* ---------- UBICACIÓN ---------- */
    .ubica { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; }
    .dir { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .horario-titulo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 21px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      margin: 30px 0 10px;
      color: var(--hueso);
    }
    .horarios { width: 100%; max-width: 420px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 15px; }
    .horarios th, .horarios td { padding: 9px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); text-align: left; }
    .horarios th { font-weight: 500; color: var(--hueso); }
    .horarios td { color: var(--muted); text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th, .horarios tr.hoy td { color: var(--carbon); background: var(--rojo-bright); font-weight: 600; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th::after {
      content: "hoy";
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: var(--carbon);
      color: var(--hueso);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2px 7px;
      margin-left: 10px;
      vertical-align: 1px;
    }
    .mapa-col { display: grid; gap: 16px; }
    .mapa iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 300px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: block;
      filter: grayscale(0.35) contrast(1.05);
    }
    .facade-photo { max-width: 320px; }

    /* ---------- CTA FINAL ---------- */
    .banda { background: var(--rojo); color: var(--hueso); padding: 60px 0; text-align: center; }
    .banda-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 8vw, 58px);
      line-height: 0.98;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }
    .banda-sub { margin: 0 auto 24px; max-width: 42ch; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(231, 226, 217, 0.92); }
    .banda .cta-row { justify-content: center; }
    .btn-dark { background: var(--carbon); color: var(--hueso); }
    .btn-dark:hover { background: #232427; }
    .btn-dark-ghost { border: 2px solid rgba(231, 226, 217, 0.55); color: var(--hueso); }
    .btn-dark-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--hueso); }

    /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
    .pie { padding: 42px 0 96px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); text-align: center; }
    .pie-logo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 28px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      color: var(--hueso);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .pie-dato { margin: 4px 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }
    .pie-dato a { color: var(--hueso); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rojo-bright); }
    .pie-dato a:hover { color: var(--rojo-bright); }
    .pie-mini { margin: 14px 0 0; color: #6f6a5e; font-size: 12px; }

    /* ---------- REVEAL (solo con JS) ---------- */
    html.js .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(16px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    html.js .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    /* ---------- DESKTOP ---------- */
    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      .heavybag { display: block; }
      .sec { padding: 104px 0; }
      .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr; }
      .offer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; }
      .reviews { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); align-items: start; }
      .ubica { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr; align-items: start; }
      .mapa iframe { height: 340px; }
      .mapa-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .facade-photo { max-width: none; }
    }
  </style>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      var d = document;
      d.documentElement.classList.add('js');

      // Resaltar el día de hoy en la tabla de horarios
      var hoy = new Date().getDay(); // 0 = domingo
      var fila = d.querySelector('.horarios tr[data-dia="' + hoy + '"]');
      if (fila) fila.classList.add('hoy');

      // Scroll-reveal (mejora progresiva)
      var els = d.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
      if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
        var io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
          entries.forEach(function (e) {
            if (e.isIntersecting) {
              e.target.classList.add('in');
              io.unobserve(e.target);
            }
          });
        }, { threshold: 0.12, rootMargin: '0px 0px -8% 0px' });
        els.forEach(function (el) { io.observe(el); });
      } else {
        els.forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('in'); });
      }
    })();
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
